imdb.plot: In the happy and delicious realm responsible for food all over the world, Cookingdom, the Recipebons are stolen from the Bundles, which protect the preparation procedures of each type of dish, subsequently targeting the food fairi...

episodes.title: Food Brings Smiles Transform! Cure Precious!"
episodes.plot: Nagomi Yui, who lives in Oishiina Town, meets Rosemary and Komekome who came from CooKingdom. But when a thief from Bundle Gang appears to steal the Recipe Book, Yui gains the power to transform into a Pretty Cure.

episodes.title: Goodbye, Yui! Mari-chan's Decision
episodes.plot: Rosemary's Delicious Stone is broken, so he can no longer use his powers. Yui says she'll fight, but Rosemary doesn't want her to get involved.

episodes.title: Kome-Kome's Errand! Lost Baby Commotion!"
episodes.plot: Kome-Kome goes on an errand by herself, hoping to make Yui happy. However, after not being able to make a purchase, Fuwa Kokone approaches her.

episodes.title: Growing Desire... Birth of Cure Spicy!"
episodes.plot: It's a new semester, and Yui is in the same class as Kokone. When Kokone, who rarely speaks to other students, interacts with Yui, she realizes Yui was the Pretty Cure from the other day.

episodes.title: I Want To Get Close To Them...! Kokone's First Friends!
episodes.plot: Rosemary thinks Kokone is avoiding him, however, Kokone just doesn't know how to interact with her new friends. Yui decides to invite Kokone and Rosemary so they can make lunch together.

episodes.title: School! Monster! Big Panic!? Target: Fried Shrimp!
episodes.plot: Although she has become friends with Yui, Kokone has yet to open up to the other students. Worried, Pam-Pam visits the school, but a rumor is going around saying "a monster was seen in the home economics room".

episodes.title: Hot Passion! Shine: Cure Yum-Yum!!
episodes.plot: Yui and the others visit Panda Hut, and become friends with their classmate, Hanamichi Ran. Ran wants to meet the Recipepes so she starts a "half-price campaign for 2 items". However.

episodes.title: Chururin Graduation!? Trip Around Oishiina Town"
episodes.plot: Ran learns that her posts on CureSta may have been influencing the Bundoru Gang. During the "Oishiina Town Walking Tour", Ran reveals that she will stop using CureSta.

episodes.title: Disagreement Between The Two Girls? Combination of Kokone and Ran!
episodes.plot: While Kokone and Ran struggle to get along, Yui invites her friends to a Takoyaki Party. However, during the party, Kokone and Ran continue having subtle disagreements.

episodes.title: Don't cry, Recipepe... Birth! Heart Juicy Mixer
episodes.plot: Yui and her friends meet the Omurice Recipepe and Kasai Amane while at a Omurice Shop. But then, the Recipepes are captured. Yui and the others struggle to defeat the strong Ubauzo, so what will they do!?
